    "description": {
      "value": "When you or a creature within 30 ft. of you takes damage, you can use your reaction to reduce that damage by [[/roll 1d10   + @prof]]. You can use this benefit [[ @prof]] times, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.\n<details>\n  <summary>\n    More Details\n  </summary>\n  <p>\n    </p><p>You can channel cosmic forces of good to gain these benefits:</p>\n<p><strong>Ability Score Increase.</strong> Increase an ability score of your choice by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p>\n<p><strong>Soothe Pain.</strong> When you or a creature within 30 feet of you takes damage, you can use your reaction to reduce that damage by 1d10 + your proficiency bonus. You can use this benefit a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, and you regain all expended uses when you finish a long rest.</p>\n  <p></p>\n</details>",
